Former media aide to Ekiti State Governor and People’s Democratic Party chieftain, Lere Olayinka has taken a swipe at former Lagos State NURTW boss, Musiliu Adesanya popularly known as MC Oluomo over his recent tweet.
MC Oluomo, who is an ardent follower of Bola Ahmed Tinubu had in a recent tweet stated that with certificate or no certificate, Bola Tinubu, who is the National Leader of the All Progressives Congress (APC) is Nigeria’s next President.
Reacting to the recent tweet, Lere Olayinka who is known for his outspokenness noted that MC Oluomo whose children are in Universities in Canada and the United States of America is in Lagos State telling people ‘who certificate help’.
The recent post by Lere Olayinka on his verified Facebook page has generated a lot of reactions from his fans and numerous followers on the social media platform.


